descriptionHtml:
This here is Myrra, I created her for my mage run through. 
You will take control of her right after Character Creation. If you use her, upload some screen-shots of what route you chose for her if you ever have the time.

You will need these mods below to get the look in the screens.
XCE -Xenius Character enhancement - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2356
Beauty Faces for Females - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1329
CBBE - Very optional. - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666



In the other picture the armor I\'m using is http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2738
author: spike1919
